    <title type="html"><![CDATA[DatePickerで入力した日付をラベルに表示する]]></title>
    <link href="http://lab.dolice.net/blog/2013/04/02/objc-date-picker/"/>
    <updated>2013-04-02T18:54:00+09:00</updated>
    <id>http://lab.dolice.net/blog/2013/04/02/objc-date-picker</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>DatePickerで指定した日付をラベルに表示するサンプルを作成しました。DatePickerで選んだ日付が指定したフォーマットで表示されます。</p>

<h2>サンプルダウンロード</h2>

<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/masakihirokawa/objc-date-picker">https://github.com/masakihirokawa/objc-date-picker</a></li>
</ul>


<h2>必要な手順</h2>

<ol>
<li>DatePickerを MainStoryboardに配置しヘッダファイルと接続します</li>
<li>日付を表示するための UILabelを配置し、ヘッダファイルにプロパティ定義します</li>
</ol>


<h2>ソースコード</h2>

<h3>ViewController.h</h3>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="c1">//ラベルを定義</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">@property</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">weak</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">nonatomic</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="kt">IBOutlet</span> <span class="n">UILabel</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">dateLabel</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="c1">//DatePickerを定義</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">@property</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">weak</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">nonatomic</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="kt">IBOutlet</span> <span class="n">UIDatePicker</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">myDatePicker</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="c1">//DatePickerを操作した時のイベントを定義</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">IBAction</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nl">changeDate:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">id</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">sender</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<h3>ViewController.m</h3>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="k">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">IBAction</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nf">changeDate:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">id</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nv">sender</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="c1">//初期化</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="n">NSDateFormatter</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[[</span><span class="n">NSDateFormatter</span> <span class="n">alloc</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="n">init</span><span class="p">];</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>  <span class="c1">//日付のフォーマット指定</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">dateFormat</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">@&quot;yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm&quot;</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>  <span class="c1">//ラベルに日付を表示</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">dateLabel</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">text</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">df</span> <span class="nl">stringFromDate:</span><span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">myDatePicker</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">date</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>
]]></content>
